## Description

Merges in work by @Mause on a CiviCRM contact loader and adds the `.greenkite` file needed for CI/CD.

The CiviCRM contact loader sits in its own subdirectory - `/src/extensions/contact-loaders/civicrm` - and thus should be safe from any future syncs with upstream. The contact loader does require the npm package `civicrm` though; `package.json` has been modified accordingly.

This has been tested on our dev instance and has worked as expected. It is ready for use in a production context.
